{"tid":2207622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部發言人汪文斌: 美國在指責別人前應當先反躬自省","createTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:29:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"338a70a055fcb33deb54e391c7a0820254f1bebe","tid":2207622,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"主管東亞事務的美國助理國務卿史迪威，在美國參議院外交關係委員會聽證會上，批評中方對基於規則的國際秩序構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌說，美國在指責別人之前，應當先反躬自省，指誰毀約退群，誰是國際規則的破壞者、對國際秩序構成威脅，國際社會看得清清楚楚，中國堅定維護以聯合國為核心的國際體系，以國際法為基礎的國際秩序，呼籲各國一同抵制單邊霸凌和保護主義，堅持多邊理念，採取多邊行動，遵守多邊協議，強化多邊機構，共同推動構建人類命運共同體。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國駐華大使布蘭斯塔德下月離任，汪文斌說，希望對方今後繼續為中美關係健康發展，發揮積極作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550373-20200918.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550373-20200918.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=17839ecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550373-20200918.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2c0e20e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550373-20200918.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"137e6c9a4fef27881c29a01d853e1aa10d4d22b4","tid":2207622,"uid":52594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大力度制裁美日歐台澳加，唔好等！唔好比生意佢地，唔好幫佢地生產。<br />\n<br />\n記住：人地錯哂"},{"pid":"9bbb7525f36095f817661e99372f0a55bf5cc07c","tid":2207622,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"美國助理國務卿：<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">中國是「目無法紀的惡霸」</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2206876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2206876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"961e58bc9329024f6169e8121a6f14f0926d57a0","tid":22076